        <label>FIGURE 1</label>
        <caption>
          <p>&#x201C;Racket&#x201D; lesion: Circular plaque with papulous well-defi ned borders in the
medial dorsal region of the left hand. Signifi cant thickening of the dorsal
branch of the radial nerve (arrow)</p>
        </caption>
        <graphic xlink:href="abd-90-03-0420-g01"/>
      </fig>
      <fig id="f02" orientation="portrait" position="float">
